title: IAlarm5 (Interface)
text:
INTERFACE IAlarm5 EXTENDS
IAlarm4
This is an extension of the IAlarm4 interface that adds setters and getters for the Offsets of Acknowledge, Active, Inactive and Last of an Alarm.
